"de desarrollo y disponible en la variable de entorno ``PATH``. Debe ser una "
"versión >= 3.5 para poder apuntar a la arquitectura ``arm64``."

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`Fuse <https://github.com/libfuse/libfuse>`__ for mounting and unmounting "
"the dmg image."
msgstr ""
"`Fuse <https://github.com/libfuse/libfuse>`__ para montar y desmontar la "
"imagen dmg."

msgid ""
"`darling-dmg <https://github.com/darlinghq/darling-dmg>`__, which needs to "
